Alright.

320
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:54,760
Here.

321
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:10,360
Are you okay?

322
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:15,200
We're almost there.

323
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,800
I don't understand.

324
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:36,960
Why did you do that?

325
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,000
What benefit does

326
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,600
offending Ding Dezhong bring to you?

327
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,320
I have offended him enough already.

328
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,700
One more time won't make a difference.

329
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,880
He bullied Afang, demoted Bai Lan,

330
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:48,780
and framed Dajiang up.

331
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:50,420
I should've settled this score with him
long ago.

332
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,080
There's a saying,

333
00:16:53,090 --> 00:16:54,280
"It's easy to deal with a gentleman,

334
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:55,680
but hard to guard against a villain."

335
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,400
Someone like Ding Dezhong

336
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,160
will make sure to get back at you.

337
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:00,440
What am I afraid of?

338
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,040
I'm leaving soon anyway.

339
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:03,600
I will be so far away from him.

340
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,880
Can he reach Shanghai?

341
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:12,720
What?

342
00:17:13,080 --> 00:17:14,040
You don't think I can pass,

343
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:14,920
do you?

344
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,960
Believe it or not,

345
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,520
in the two practice exams,

346
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:20,040
I was first in the whole class.

347
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,280
Really?

348
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:22,520
See?

349
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,840
That's my son.

350
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,480
My son is smart of course.

351
00:17:26,080 --> 00:17:27,000
If you don't pass this year,

352
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:27,960
you'll try again next year.

353
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,040
Xiaolu,

354
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,640
it's not that I don't support you,

355
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:38,120
but you need to be mentally prepared.

356
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,040
For what?

357
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,880
I just received news that

358
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:44,440
this time the factory

359
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:45,960
only has one spot

360
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:47,840
for study in Shanghai.

361
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:56,560
Secretary Hong!

362
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:00,400
Secretary Hong!

363
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,000
Secretary Hong is out of town.

364
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:13,640
What's the matter?

365
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:15,680
Let me ask you,

366
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:17,600
is it true that there's only one spot

367
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:18,440
for studying abroad

368
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:19,400
this year?

369
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:22,160
You're well-informed.

370
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,280
Why?

371
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:25,510
There were always three to five spots
available in previous years,

372
00:18:25,650 --> 00:18:26,480
but why not this year?

373
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,960
The factory's performance isn't good
this year.

374
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,680
If we lose more workers now,

375
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,680
it'll only make people more unsettled.

376
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,680
Everyone wants to leave.

377
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:37,480
What will the factory do?

378
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,200
It'll just become an empty shell.

379
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:41,920
No way.

380
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:43,360
Don't lie to me.

381
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:46,920
Call Secretary Hong yourself

382
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,240
and see if it's true.

383
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:01,080
I know you want to leave.

384
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:05,040
This place is like stagnant water,

385
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,320
dreary,

386
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,000
oppressive,

387
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,280
suffocating.

388
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,840
Who doesn't want to leave?

389
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:21,600
But who can escape?

390
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:30,960
Some things

391
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:33,000
are destined from birth.

392
00:19:34,280 --> 00:19:35,320
You can't escape,

393
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,120
and neither can I.

394
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:40,880
What about next year?

395
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,520
Just wait and see.

396
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:52,760
Everything will only get tighter

397
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:55,560
as the factory

398
00:19:58,040 --> 00:19:59,880
gets through this rough patch.

399
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:04,960
How long do we have to wait?

400
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,640
Maybe

401
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:09,880
next year,

402
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,760
maybe...

