405
00:21:19,140 --> 00:21:23,340
♪All diaries are locked♪

406
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:26,110
♪Don't care♪

407
00:21:27,560 --> 00:21:28,400
Staying here

408
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,000
