409
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:32,440
(1997 Self-Study Exam Application Form)
of Director Bi and people like him.

410
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,320
Only by going to a bigger world

411
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:37,440
will you find freedom.

412
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:43,600
I can't stand it here anymore.

413
00:21:44,010 --> 00:21:46,620
♪This kind of emotion♪

414
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,680
Do you think we'll be able to

415
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:50,840
(Lu Xiaolu)
successfully make it to Shanghai?

416
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,000
Of course.

417
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,280
If it weren't for you,

418
00:21:54,560 --> 00:21:55,480
I might never take

419
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,640
the college entrance exam again.

420
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,820
Will we have our own home in Shanghai?

421
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:01,440
Definitely.

422
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:05,000
♪Not buries anymore♪

423
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:11,890
♪Cause I said♪

424
00:22:12,330 --> 00:22:15,180
♪This is why I stay♪

425
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:19,160
We were all going direct to heaven.

426
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:23,960
We were all going direct the other way.

427
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:25,960
You startled me

428
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:27,960
