446
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,080
Really?

447
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,520
Even you didn't know?

448
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:04,200
I thought it was just me.

449
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:05,680
Today, they told me that

450
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:07,440
foreigners only eat rare,

451
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,520
medium, medium-well,

452
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:11,120
and well-done steaks.

453
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:14,440
Wow, you know quite a lot.

454
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,360
That's so troublesome.

455
00:23:16,840 --> 00:23:17,880
Just remember,

456
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:19,960
don't embarrass yourself

457
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,920
when we get to Shanghai.

458
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,960
Okay, after we get to Shanghai,

459
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:24,800
I'll stick with you.

460
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,160
I'm wondering,

461
00:23:39,120 --> 00:23:41,160
