466
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:52,280
We can be beggars.

467
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,800
You are so handsome.

468
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:55,400
So you might be able
to make a lot of money.

469
00:23:58,800 --> 00:23:59,800
The steak is done.

470
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,480
Why are you worrying so much today?

471
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:06,040
You have never been like this.

472
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:06,880
Nothing.

473
00:24:07,760 --> 00:24:09,360
The exam is just in the next month,

474
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,520
so I thought about

475
00:24:13,080 --> 00:24:15,040
many things
that might happen in the future.

476
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,000
Don't worry.

477
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,920
We can always do part-time jobs
in Shanghai.

478
00:24:19,180 --> 00:24:20,620
We won't really end up
begging on the streets.

479
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,480
Enjoy it while it's hot.

480
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:29,440
Let me ask you something.

481
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:32,760
If,

482
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,400
I mean if,

483
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:37,320
I don't make it to Shanghai,

484
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:40,760
