485
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:41,720
Yes, I can.

486
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,720
You agreed so quickly,

487
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,080
you didn't even ask me why.

488
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:47,400
As long as you're trying your best,

489
00:24:48,040 --> 00:24:49,000
I'm willing to wait for you.

490
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:58,080
I'm so relieved.

491
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:00,120
For what?

492
00:25:03,360 --> 00:25:04,440
For everything.

493
00:25:07,080 --> 00:25:08,760
You are strange today.

494
00:25:17,360 --> 00:25:18,240
Tastes good.

495
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:23,520
This eighty percent well steak

496
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:24,680
is surprisingly good.

497
00:25:25,280 --> 00:25:26,640
Because it was made by an amazing chef.

498
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:42,160
To Shanghai!

499
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:43,880
To us!

500
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:54,640
Why are you being so deep?

501
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,160
I'll be back in a few days.

502
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,240
I'm not.

503
00:25:57,760 --> 00:25:58,880
I just want to see you more.

504
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:00,920
I think you are particularly

505
00:26:01,520 --> 00:26:02,360
beautiful today.

506
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,240
What's wrong with you?

507
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:05,480
I am beautiful every day.

508
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:07,680
Yes, you're right,

509
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,200
but today, you look especially chic,

510
00:26:09,560 --> 00:26:10,720
