511
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,000
Alright, go back now.

512
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:16,560
Rest well and study for the exams.

513
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:18,280
Remember to drink more milk.

514
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,240
You too.

515
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:22,280
I'm leaving now.

516
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:29,960
