540
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,400
Why isn't it listed?

541
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,520
That can't be true. It must be a rumor.

542
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:38,120
Yeah, it's definitely a rumor.

543
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:40,560
Oh, buddy,

544
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:41,920
