545
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:43,400
You'll do better next time.

546
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:09,760
Bro, I'll come back tomorrow.

547
00:29:09,760 --> 00:29:11,120
Okay, come earlier tomorrow.

548
00:29:11,120 --> 00:29:11,960
Okay.

