♪Lies in silence♪

858
00:53:01,780 --> 00:53:03,940
♪Don't forget that I once had you♪

859
00:53:03,940 --> 00:53:07,100
♪You once loved me too♪

860
00:53:09,220 --> 00:53:11,220
♪When you left me♪

861
00:53:11,220 --> 00:53:14,790
♪The pain I didn't want to accept♪

862
00:53:15,200 --> 00:53:20,240
♪Love in the end is still a dream♪

863
00:53:22,230 --> 00:53:25,090
♪Don't say our worlds♪

864
00:53:25,090 --> 00:53:28,720
♪Are too different♪

865
00:53:29,090 --> 00:53:31,250
♪Just say you've forgotten me♪

866
00:53:31,250 --> 00:53:35,580
♪You're about to leave me♪

867
00:53:35,960 --> 00:53:39,100
♪Who can tell me♪

868
00:53:39,100 --> 00:53:42,510
♪If I gave too much♪

869
00:53:42,770 --> 00:53:46,000
♪Just pretend I never existed♪

870
00:53:46,000 --> 00:53:49,750
♪Or disappear from my heart♪

871
00:53:49,750 --> 00:53:52,750
♪Who once reminded me♪

872
00:53:52,750 --> 00:53:56,210
♪My love had no certainty♪

873
00:53:56,440 --> 00:53:59,600
♪Just pretend I never had it♪

874
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:06,350
♪Forget you, forget me♪

875
00:54:43,010 --> 00:54:45,520
♪Will I miss the beat♪

876
00:54:45,520 --> 00:54:47,670
♪Will I disturb this tenderness♪

877
00:54:47,970 --> 00:54:50,310
♪Pretending not to care is fake♪

878
00:54:50,310 --> 00:54:52,690
♪In this, I have a talent♪

879
00:54:53,070 --> 00:54:55,330
♪You and I walk side by side, far apart♪

880
00:54:55,550 --> 00:54:57,790
♪Truth is hidden in my pretentious words♪

881
00:54:57,790 --> 00:54:59,690
♪The seagulls have come♪

882
00:54:59,690 --> 00:55:03,380
♪Flapping their wings,
laughing at my confusion♪

883
00:55:03,740 --> 00:55:06,090
♪A life unchanged♪

884
00:55:06,090 --> 00:55:08,220
♪No waves, no crests♪

885
00:55:08,500 --> 00:55:11,380
♪Then this day suddenly appears♪

886
00:55:11,380 --> 00:55:13,040
♪With clear outlines♪

887
00:55:13,040 --> 00:55:14,880
♪And I panic♪

888
00:55:14,880 --> 00:55:17,950
♪As if possessed♪

889
00:55:17,950 --> 00:55:19,800
♪Examining my life♪

890
00:55:19,800 --> 00:55:23,640
♪Seems I've dodged too much♪

891
00:55:23,640 --> 00:55:26,850
♪So please don't leave me alone♪

892
00:55:26,850 --> 00:55:28,200
♪Sad and cold♪

893
00:55:28,200 --> 00:55:32,000
♪I think everybody knows, but you♪

894
00:55:32,000 --> 00:55:34,300
♪Being with you is my happiness♪

895
00:55:34,300 --> 00:55:37,030
♪I look forward to your attention♪

896
00:55:37,030 --> 00:55:39,350
♪Counting every memory♪

897
00:55:39,350 --> 00:55:43,300
♪Joy always accompanies pain♪

898
00:55:43,300 --> 00:55:45,820
♪So let me shout it out♪

899
00:55:45,820 --> 00:55:48,340
♪I think I'll make you proud♪

900
00:55:48,340 --> 00:55:51,010
♪Nobody tell me what to do♪

901
00:55:51,010 --> 00:55:53,440
♪My life is not a boring loop♪

902
00:55:53,440 --> 00:55:55,960
♪This time I'm not joking♪

903
00:55:55,960 --> 00:55:58,430
♪The taste of hitting rock bottom♪

904
00:55:58,690 --> 00:56:01,410
♪From now on, following your steps♪

905
00:56:01,410 --> 00:56:04,720
♪Solving the question in my heart♪

